Former BBNaija “Lockdown” housemate, ‘Erica’ Nlewedim has expressed gratitude for an unanswered prayer. In her tweet, Star girl, who’ll be 28 in a couple of days, revealed she is grateful for not having received an answer to her prayer on getting married at 23 which she has now termed ‘foolish’.   Dating Kanye West best thing that happened to me –…     I’m considering dropping out of Oxford University – DJ Cuppy     Segun Arinze to youths: get active in politics   She made this known in her response to her colleague, Adesua Etomi’s tweet where she thanked God for not having answered her foolish prayers. “Lord it’s me. Just here to say thank you for not answering my foolish prayers because…” Etomi tweeted. Erica, who was in sync with Adesua Etomi’s tweet, went to say: “Exactly!! Especially the ones about getting married at 23!”